Body: ⚙ATF Manufacturing And Production  👇 Today our team wanted to share with you the details about our production, manufacturing of equipment and general information about our daily life!  As we do not have our own production so far, we are dependent on the third-party contractors in industrial cities, such as Yekaterinburg in Russia, where the industrial manufacturing is in a high specialization. Author: AgroTechFarmOfficial
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: This is a real manufacture of home and industrial equipment for the automatized organic products cultivation all year round everywhere in the world and by any climatic conditions.  The lack of ecologically green and harmless products is the planet-scale problem. According to the World Health Organization, dangerous food could be the reason of more than 200 illnesses, from gastrointestinal disturbance to oncology. By estimate of the organization, every year 600 million people, almost every 6th planet habitant, get ill due to the reason. The growing global demand on the organic products is satisfied less than by 1%, which causes dangerous conditions to the human’s health. The organic products retail is more than $81 billion per year. 90% of the products are sold in the North America and Europe. The demand is gradually growing also in Asia, Latin America and Africa.  The ATF equipment can solve such problems as: -the lack of natural and organic products at the market -absence of fresh products in the countries with bad climatic conditions, where the cultivation of vegetables and berries isn’t possible -impossibility to grow vegetables and get fresh products in metropolises -necessity to provide acres of loam for vegetables cultivation -logistic expenses by products delivery  We have taken a poll in order to estimate the organic products demand at the Europe and the USA market. We have seen a huge demand on our equipment especially in the countries where cannabis is legalized. The size of the North American market of cannabis was more than $7 billion in 2017; the projected growth is estimated for more than $22 billion to 2021.  “Brightfield Group” predicts the volume of the global cannabis market to reach $31 billion to 2020. With the ATF equipment we are entering the fast growing cannabis market, which allows a private person to get the wanted product and to compensate the equipment costs in 6 months.

Author: AgroTechFarmOfficial
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: Ilya Tsigvintsev  Founder and CEO  Moscow International Business School. Economist. Founder of the «AgroTechFarm» company. Ilya is the initiator of the product ATF elaboration and establishment. He organized the micro treatment production. Business experience is 15 years long. He was engaged in building machinery trading, construction material production, tender delivering for state-owned enterprises; he also founded a video facilities installation company.  The inner ATF technology is based on hydroponics and enhanced solid-state lightning. Hydroponics is the method of growing plants without soil. Hydroponics systems perfectly pass for a commercial producer because they are highly efficient and don’t need huge assets; moreover they provide higher crop yield alongside with reduced labor.  http://www.picshare.ru/uploads/180506/rhuV653Ust.jpg

Author: AgroTechFarmOfficial
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: The ATF equipment perfectly passes for automatic cannabis cultivation. Today the demand on cannabis appeared in such countries as the USA and Canada is growing fast. Despite the huge efforts of national marijuana producers there is a hefty shortage of efficient equipment which caters to the needs of customers. Some big producers are not able to satisfy the existing demand due to the insufficient production. As a result there is a promising opportunity for satisfying the boosting need for the organic products and obvious demand on all types of equipment using the particular method of agricultural crop cultivation.  Currently the “ATF Home Grower” company stands in as the simple solution. It makes the cultivating process easier for an average consumer, what positively affects the situation development. According to the most researches, the obvious growth of sale of marijuana for recreational use is expected. For sellers and investors the cannabis trading business could be a new boom. The ATF team has some years of special experience in elaboration and manufacturing of agricultural equipment. The market conditions and regulation changes provide the unique opportunity which ATF can exploit to the fullest.

Author: AgroTechFarmOfficial
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: There is the list of advantages of Agro Tech Farm:  - Automated short growing cycle of plants in light of an optimal balance of water and fertilizers in collaboration with defined efficient LED lights. - A scheme of two vegetation cells installed inside the appliance presenting an option to get the yield of two large plants in sequence. Thus, there is no need for the customer to have a long waiting period as suggested by our competitors. Two vegetative cells may spontaneously provide customers with fresh organic cannabis harvest every week. - ATF farm is the only one manufacturer who focuses the complete automation of the vegetative processes occurring inside the appliance. It means that there is no necessity to conduct numerous checkups of pH level, carbon filters rotation, TDS calibration, nutrient cartridges replacement. The only activities you have to commit to are to plant the seeds and harvest your crops. You should also clean it twice a year and when nutrients run low add them (every 2-3 months). - There is no additional hidden maintenance cost which appears to be quite unexpected for users. ATF buyers get a free set of supplements covering needs in nutrition for one year at least. - An elegant design makes ATF home a new distinguishable part, considerably individualizing your residential interior and attracting attention of guests. - ATF farms are covered by a 2-year manufacturer warranty. - Unlike substantial number of new teams applying for ICO funding, ATF team accumulated serious experience in indoor cultivation and home farms design and production.

Author: aquacharls
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: With the help of a nutrient meter, the grower has also the ability to fully monitor and maintain a relative consistency throughout the process. Nutrient composition is key for the process. Manual mixing can be quite difficult, since there are over twenty elements needed for plant growth. The basic elements, carbon, hydrogen and oxygen, are absorbed from air and water. The rest of the elements, called mineral nutrients, are dissolved in the nutrient solution and require are needed in specific proportions. Any good hydroponic nutrient solution must contain all of these elements: Nitrogen (N),Potassium (K), Phosphorous (P),Calcium (Ca), Magnesium (Mg), Sulphur (S), Iron (Fe), Manganese (Mn), Copper (Cu), Zinc (Zn), Molybdenum (Mo), Boron (B), Chlorine (Cl). For the most part, this is taken care of with any pre-formulated commercial hydroponic nutrients. Often, these pre-made nutrients come in one, two, three or even more “parts” so the grower can change the ratio of the mineral elements to allow for either vegetables, fruits or flowers to grow, and for different crops.

Author: aquacharls
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: The Cannabis plant has been used for thousands of years by many cultures, for medical and spiritual purposes, but also for recreational uses. For example, a bag of Cannabis has been found in a shaman’s grave in China, dated more than 2700 years old. This and other facts point to Asia as Cannabis’ natural origins.  The Greek historian Herodotus mentions the plant being used by Scythians in cannabis steam baths and thus gives us the first written record of Cannabis use at around 440 BC. Up until the beginning of the 20th century, the plant has been considered as socially acceptable in many cultures, especially when used for religious and spiritual ceremonies. A common form of ‘decriminalization’, now practiced in some countries, such as the US, Australia and Europe, is using fines to punish users. This retains the presumed advantage of withholding state approval while reducing social costs and the legal consequences of criminal convictions.

Author: aquacharls
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: A legal market for recreational marijuana could give Canada’s economy a boost of up to $22.6 billion annually, says a new study from business services firm Deloitte. The study estimates that marijuana sales, even initially, would be at least as large as hard liquor sales in Canada, at around $5 billion annually, but could be as large as $8.7 billion, making them as large as wine sales. The total impact for Canada’s economy of legal cannabis market — including growing and distribution, pot paraphernalia, increased tourism and business taxes — would amount to between $12.7 billion to $22.6 billion annually. The Canadian marijuana market is expected to grow fast in the coming years: it is still well under-penetrated, leaving room for significant growth and potential new entrants. Mackie Research Capital Corporation forecasts the peak Canadian marijuana market size to be over $2.2B in 2020, assuming full legalization down the road (over $1B in 2020 without full 18 legalization) - some of these sales are being cannibalized by the black market via dispensaries. Their marijuana model assumes that the Canadian market would follow a similar growth trajectory and market penetration trend as has occurred in Colorado and Oregon.

Author: aquacharls
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: The Cannabis plant has been used for thousands of years by many cultures, for medical and spiritual purposes, but also for recreational uses. For example, a bag of Cannabis has been found in a shaman’s grave in China, dated more than 2700 years old. This and other facts point to Asia as Cannabis’ natural origins. The Greek historian Herodotus mentions the plant being used by Scythians in cannabis steam baths and thus gives us the first written record of Cannabis use at around 440 BC. Up until the beginning of the 20th century, the plant has been considered as socially acceptable in many cultures, especially when used for religious and spiritual ceremonies. A common form of ‘decriminalization’, now practiced in some countries, such as the US, Australia and Europe, is using fines to punish users. This retains the presumed advantage of withholding state approval while reducing social costs and the legal consequences of criminal convictions.

Author: aquacharls
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: LED lights are revolutionizing plant cultivation, offering numerous advantages like growth stimulation, energetic efficiency, adjustable wavelengths, and many others. The primary benefit of LED over the more common light sources is a significantly reduced heat and power consumption.  Producing less heat, LEDs are more efficient and require significantly less ventilation and cooling. Light color is also of great importance, as it will influence the plants’ well being. For instance, natural light is the best for seedlings that are just beginning to grow

Author: aquacharls
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: With the help of a nutrient meter, the grower has also the ability to fully monitor and maintain a relative consistency throughout the process. Nutrient composition is key for the process. Manual mixing can be quite difficult, since there are over twenty elements needed for plant growth. The basic elements, carbon, hydrogen and oxygen, are absorbed from air and water. The rest of the elements, called mineral nutrients, are dissolved in the nutrient solution and require are needed in specific proportions. Any good hydroponic nutrient solution must contain all of these elements: Nitrogen (N),Potassium (K), Phosphorous (P),Calcium (Ca), Magnesium (Mg), Sulphur (S), Iron (Fe), Manganese (Mn), Copper (Cu), Zinc (Zn), Molybdenum (Mo), Boron (B), Chlorine (Cl). For the most part, this is taken care of with any pre-formulated commercial hydroponic nutrients. Often, these pre-made nutrients come in one, two, three or even more “parts” so the grower can change the ratio of the mineral elements to allow for either vegetables, fruits or flowers to grow, and for different crops.

Author: AgroTechFarmOfficial
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: A short history of Agro Tech Farm  Today we want to tell you more about the history of our company as a sign of openness and respect for our future investors. https://i.imgur.com/7Kr0exy.jpg We, the founders of AgroTechFarm, started work in the field of automated cultivation to increase the yield of existing farms as early as in 2013. Back then our technologist Alexey Kovnerchuk patented the first development of a device for hydroponic growing. Our longstanding goal was to goal was to create a fully automated industrial machine for growing plants.  Back in 2014 with the geopolitical event of Crimea, russia was cut off from the world by sanctions. As a retributional step, russia decided to sanction imports, which hit the agricultural sector especially hard.  However, for russian entrepreneurs this opened an opportunity and a door to innovation. Since the supply was quasi decreased overnight, but demand didn’t change, prices for agricultural products started to rise.  We saw the opportunity and started to work on a vertical growing solution to increase the yield of existing farms a  In 2017 we met another company that had a very similar mission as we and we decided to cooperate with them, the name of the company was OOO Agronomov with the brand fibonacci (fibonacci.farm). At the time their product was still not working. We thought that with united forces we might solve this problem. This is why we decided to invest in the Agronomof company because they needed funds for further development in exchange we secured the rights to distribute the machines in eastern Russia as exclusive partner. However, the company did not fulfill its obligations rather the employees were not paid their salaries and our invested money was spent for unknown activities and subsequently the company is in the process of closing.  We sued the company Agronomof because of their activities. There are several lawsuits pending for the company at the moment. The founder Baranov Alexey has Multimillion-dollar debts outstanding and it’s currently not allowed to leave the country, as can be verified through public information. The damage is estimated at 15.000.000 rubles.  Nevertheless, we decided to continue the work on the products of Fibonacci under our own company. Many former employees of Fibonacci joined our team. Since then we have improved the machine and it is now working and we have applied for a new patent.  Come and visit our showroom in Ekaterinburg Russia or our website: https://www.agrotechfarm.io  If you have any questions please do not hesitate to contact us

Body: Here’s how hydroponic vertical growth works.The roots grow down through a cup. The nutrient solution is pumped into the cell medium, floods the root zone for a short time, and is then allowed to drain back into the reservoir. A consistent power supply is critical, since all systems require electrical power (to run water or air pumps). With strict control and automation of the processes, they become almost user-independent and fail-proof.

Body: Our approach formed on a combination of hydroponics with LED lighting to secure the optimal way for plant growing. All plants get nutrient supplements mixed with water along with air. The hydroponics method stimulates plants to grow faster as compared to the traditional agricultural approach. A balanced nutrient solution contains such macro elements as nitrogen (N), phosphorus (P), calcium (Ca), sulfur (S) e.t.c. All additives used in hydroponics ideally feed plants, unlike natural soil, which is not capable of producing a large amount of nutrients ideal for plant growth. The scripted system provides the required quantity of supplements to plant roots.  And Yes, in comparison with the majority of ICO projects we have already developed and tested an ATF agro appliance. Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: Manual mixing can be quite difficult, since there are over twenty elements needed for plant growth. The basic elements, carbon, hydrogen and oxygen, are absorbed from air and water. The rest of the elements, called mineral nutrients, are dissolved in the nutrient solution and require are needed in specific proportions. Any good hydroponic nutrient solution must contain all of these elements: Nitrogen (N),Potassium (K), Phosphorous (P),Calcium (Ca), Magnesium (Mg), Sulphur (S), Iron (Fe), Manganese (Mn), Copper (Cu), Zinc (Zn), Molybdenum (Mo), Boron (B), Chlorine (Cl)

Body: The current moment both US and Canada markets are relatively young and not saturated, despite a significant rise of cannabis consumers. ATF Home Grower is a brand-new home appliance differentiates from the few existing, not market ready labels by the following features:  Automated short growing cycle of plants in light of an optimal balance of water and fertilizers in collaboration with defined efficient LED lights. A scheme of two vegetation cells installed inside the appliance presenting an option to get the yield of two large plants in sequence. Thus, there is no need for the customer to have a long waiting period as suggested by our competitors. Two vegetative cells may spontaneously provide customers with fresh organic cannabis harvest every week. ATF farm is the only one manufacturer who focuses the complete automation of the vegetative processes occurring inside the appliance. It means that there is no necessity to conduct numerous checkups of pH level, carbon filters rotation, TDS calibration, nutrient cartridges replacement. The only activities you have to commit to are to plant the seeds and harvest your crops. You should also clean it twice a year and when nutrients run low add them (every 2-3 months). There is no additional hidden maintenance cost which appears to be quite unexpected for users. ATF buyers get a free set of supplements covering needs in nutrition for one year at least. An elegant design makes ATF home a new distinguishable part, considerably individualizing your residential interior and attracting attention of guests. ATF farms are covered by a 2-year manufacturer warranty. Unlike substantial number of new teams applying for ICO funding, ATF team accumulated serious experience in indoor cultivation and home farms design and production.

Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: ATF Home Grower is a fully automated indoor appliance for cannabis and other vegetable cultivation at home. Does neither require any specific knowledge nor professional skills in crops growing. Based on ATF team substantial experience in industrial hydroponics and LED grow lighting, all technologies are safe, efficient and sustainable providing customers with rich organic product yield shortly. All agricultural cycles related to the growth and harvest of a crop are running automatically and may be easily monitored via Smartphone.  Our approach formed on a combination of hydroponics with LED lighting to secure the optimal way for plant growing. All plants get nutrient supplements mixed with water along with air.  The hydroponics method stimulates plants to grow faster as compared to the traditional agricultural approach. A balanced nutrient solution contains such macro elements as nitrogen (N), phosphorus (P), calcium (Ca), sulfur (S) e.t.c. All additives used in hydroponics ideally feed plants, unlike natural soil, which is not capable of producing a large amount of nutrients ideal for plant growth. The scripted system provides the required quantity of supplements to plant roots.

Author: AlexBasov
Title: [ANN][ATF][TokenSale] – THE GLOBAL ECO BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM
Body: Hi, my name is Alex Basov. I am the founder of AgroTechFarm. Let me tell a little story about us.  Our interest in agrotechnology and the hydroponic growing method started in 2012.  In 2013, we began to work on our own solution for hydroponic technology. That same year we had already created a hydroponic grower, and applied for a patent. We assembled the appliances on our own, and conducted a few tests and grew tomatoes and peppers. The following year, in 2014, we had our patent. With that technology, we took part in Skolkovo “Clean Tech Russia 2014”, reaching the semi-finals.  By 2015, we had already set a new goal for our work: the development of a perfected domestic farm. Although the concept and project were fully developed, unfortunately, we could not reach enough funding to launch production. Veering towards industrial solutions, we took our first steps in 2016 to develop a fully automated industrial complex for growing berries and other vegetables. This was also the time that opened the road to growing micro greens.  In March, 2017, we discovered that another Russian company was working on the same problem. After getting to know the team and their project, we became enthusiasts. The product’s design was outstanding, you can see it fibonacci.farm. Regrettably, their installations were mere concepts: they were not yet functional and no production was taking place.  We ended up investing in Agronomof LLC. They had the Fibonacci brand already. They had promised to make a working product out of their concept design, but they could not deliver. Agronomof claimed a fully automated solution, but the product did not work. Importantly, they could never resolve issues with installing and mantaining the micro climate needed along with watering and light. Production never started.  Agronomof was actually a big flop. It did not pay its employees and ended up seriously misusing the investment funds. The company shut down, firing everyone. Naturally, we sued to recover at least some of our investment. Damages amounted to about 15 million rubles.  While the legal issues were being resolverd, some of Agronomof’s employees who had manifested their interest in collaborating with us joined the team. Their knowledge and experience were invaluable to us at that moment to help our project, that dated back to 2013, to finally take off.  Agronomof has a patent on its module’s technology. But the device does not work.  Our vast experience, however, pointed to an important fact: the module was part of the problem and did not let plants grow.  Together with our engineers, we switched to more advanced technologies.  We are under the process of obtaining a patent for this new solution, protecting our invention. Unlike Agronomof’s early patent, this solution, right now, works. Our growers display a LED light, a sustained microclimate, a fully automated drainage and watering systems, complete control of Ph level and even pollination.  We took Fibonacci’s design because it was elegant, functional and free to use. Of course, we are also working on some adaptations to enhance our growers’ personality.  As of today, the future looks bright. We have recently won our legal battle against Agronomof, and may recover some of our embezzled investment.  All my words can be confirmed by documents  We are proud of the team we have assembled. These top-notch professional are more than able to create a large-scale production of home farms. We have accumulated much important experience since 2012, and surmounted several hurdles along these bumpy road.  Ready to create an innovative product, we have launched the ICO certain of its success.  AgroTechFarm.IO
